<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset Email</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .ii a[href] {
            color: #fff;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #b7c8da;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #94a7ba;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <p>Dear <%=username%>,</p>

        <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account with Move Exercise. To proceed with resetting
            your password, please click on the link below:</p>

        <p><a class="button" href="<%=link%>" target="_blank">Reset
                Password</a></p>

        <p>If you did not request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your account will remain
            secure.</p>

        <p>Please note that the password reset link is valid for a limited time. If you don't use the link within 2
            minutes, you'll need to request another password reset.</p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing Move Exercise!</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,<br>Move Exercise Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>